description:
Hi, We are delighted to share our new game with you :)

Game Name: Magic Farm Mystery

Description:   A little farm boy lost his key and she is begging you for help. Your mission is to find the missing key by searching around the farm. Get his key back and solve the escape-style mystery! Good Luck and Have Fun!
